Caretaker (Star Trek: Voyager).label: Caretaker
Caretaker (Star Trek: Voyager).description: "Caretaker" is the first and second episodes of the science fiction television series Star Trek Voyager. This series pilot premiered as one double-length episode on January 16, 1995, as the first telecast of the fledgling UPN network. Wikipedia

The Naked Now.label: The Naked Now
The Naked Now.description: "The Naked Now" is the third episode of the first season of the American science fiction television series Star Trek The Next Generation, originally aired on October 5, 1987 in broadcast syndication in the United States. Wikipedia
